### Login
POST http://localhost:2000/user-api/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "ram@gmail.com",
    "password": "charan"
}

### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:2000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"Ram Charan",
    "password":"charan",
    "email":"ram@gmail.com",
    "age":20
}

